    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available for acquisition is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in pristine mechanical and cosmetic order. This example is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS variable valve timing system that operates silently. The power is delivered through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox to a limited-slip rear differential. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings were replaced as preventative maintenance. The suspension retains its factory geometry with refreshed bushings for optimal turn-in response. The exterior maintains its factory luster with no signs of oxidation or paint metered inconsistencies, while the interior leather remains supple with firm bolsters. This is a turn-key, analog performance machine for the serious collector.",
